Package: rippo
Title: Creates Content Suitable for Inclusion in AAGI IPPO Tables 2 and 3 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
 .
        )
Description: Checks a project directory and creates a CSV file suitable for
  inclusion in an AAGI IPPO Table 3. The CSV file contains a list of all R 
  packages used in the project, including their version numbers and licences along 
  with the the AAGIQuarto template information if requested.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/adamhsparks/rippo
BugReports: https://github.com/adamhsparks/rippo/issues
Imports: 
